snippet.title: Catherine: Full Body | Fine Wine Trailer
snippet.description:
The captivating tale of 2011’s award-winning Catherine returns in Catherine: Full Body, launching in the Americas and Europe on September 3, 2019!

Catherine: Full Body is bigger and better than before; improved visuals and gameplay, brand-new music, enhanced multiplayer options, and much more await in this enticing new package.

Pre-order the 'Heart's Desire' Premium Edition or Launch Edition now at https://www.catherinethegame.com/fullbody/
